snippet.title: Investing Made Simple - Nathan Sloan
snippet.description:
Welcome to Investing Made Simple with me, Nathan Sloan. 

Having worked in financial services in London for several years, I found it very common for people to over-complicate money & investing. This channel was created to simplify investing and help people build wealth.  

★ Crypto
★ Stocks 
★ Property
★ Bonds 
★ Gold & Silver 
★ Commodities 
★ Business

The Mission
➤ To help thousands of people become better off financially

Values
➤ Integrity 
➤ Simplicity 
➤ Freedom 

🏚  Official Social Media Accounts 
👉🏼 Twitter = https://twitter.com/_NathansTweet
👉🏼 YouTube = https://www.youtube.com/c/InvestingMadeSimpleHQ

ALL OTHER SOCIAL MEDIA ACCOUNTS ARE FAKE

Disclaimer: This channel is for education purposes only. You should seek investment advice from a registered professional before making any investment decision. This channel is not responsible for any investment actions taken by viewers.
